dc_title_s: Development, Edge Features: Montgomery County, Maryland, 2015
dc_description_s: This is a feature class in the geodatabase Planimetric Mapping Features: Montgomery County, Maryland, 2015. This data set contains polygonal and line features which reflect particular features resultant from development such as: athletic fields, golf courses, swimming pools etc. The data was developed as part of the planimetric mapping tasks for the County. Attributes for the data set include a name and GeoMaP created feature code number for classification.11/10/2015: Entire countywide data updated by KUCERA INTERNATIONAL. Source date: 4/10/2014 imagery
